detail_desc: Wide, sturdy belt with a metal buckle that has a stud at the back. Width 3.4 cm.
Push-up bra in lace and mesh with underwired, padded cups for a larger bust and fuller cleavage. Adjustable shoulder straps and a hook-and-eye fastening at the back.
Tube scarf in soft faux fur.
Long-sleeved blouse in an airy, floral-print viscose weave with a V-neck and wrapover with buttons at the front.
Narrow metal Alice band with cat ears on top decorated with small, faceted plastic beads.
Short jacket in washed cotton twill with a collar, buttons down the front, side pockets and long sleeves. Unlined.
Bolero in soft, textured-knit cotton with a one-button fastening at the front and long sleeves.
Sleeveless dress in an airy weave with a V-neck, pleat at the back and stand up collar with wide ties at the front. Lined.
Hat in soft rib-knit cashmere.

Super push-up bra in lace and mesh with underwired, thickly padded cups to maximise the bust and create a fuller cleavage. Narrow, adjustable shoulder straps, a wide lace trim at the hem and a hook-and-eye fastening at the back.
Short dress in slub jersey made from a modal and cotton blend. Short cap sleeves with sewn-in turn-ups, a narrow, elasticated seam at the waist, side pockets and a gently flared skirt.

Wide, turtleneck jumper in a soft, fine knit containing glittery threads with low dropped shoulders and wide sleeves with tapered cuffs. Narrow cut at the hem with high slits in the sides. Longer at the back.
Hair elastics without metal clips.
Long-sleeved tops in soft cotton jersey with a press-stud on one shoulder (except in sizes 1½-4Y) and ribbing around the neckline.
Bandeau bra in sturdy microfibre with adjustable spaghetti shoulder straps, removable inserts and soft, concealed elastication at the top and bottom. Lined at the front.

Trousers geared to outdoor activity with good air permeability to wick away moisture. The trousers are made from a stretchy woven fabric for increased mobility, with a water-repellent finish on the bum and knees. Elasticated waist for added comfort, a zip fly and button, side pockets and a diagonal, zipped leg pocket for safe storage of valuables. Reinforced, wear-resistant hems with adjustable fasteners. Unlined.

Imitation suede sandals with an ankle-height shaft and covered block heels. Lacing with wide laces that have fringed ends. Satin linings, imitation leather insoles and rubber soles. Heel approx. 8.5 cm.
V-neck top in soft organic cotton jersey with narrow shoulder straps.

Short shirt dress in a cotton weave with a collar and concealed buttons down the front. Dropped shoulder seams, long, wide sleeves with buttoned cuffs, a tapered waist with pleats, and a gently rounded hem.
Dress in soft cotton jersey with a reversible sequin motif on the front (sizes 1½-3Y with normal sequins), short, flounced sleeves, a gathered seam at the waist and a gently flared skirt.
Thong briefs in cotton jersey with a low waist, lined gusset and string back.
Shorts in stretch jersey with a denim look made from a cotton blend. Elasticated waist, fake front pockets, real back pockets and sewn-in turn-ups at the hems.
Fully lined, 5-pocket, slim-fit jeans in washed stretch denim with an adjustable elasticated waist, zip fly and press-stud and narrow hems. Jersey lining.
Sleeveless fitted top in a sturdy rib knit with a slight sheen and a V-neck front and back.
Boxy-style bomber jacket with a ribbed stand-up collar, zip down the front and diagonal front pockets with a flap and press-stud. Dropped shoulders and long, wide sleeves. Lined.
Cardigan knitted in a soft wool blend with buttons down the front.
Long-sleeved, fitted top in ribbed jersey with a slight sheen. Tape-trimmed V-neck front and back.

All-in-one suit in soft sweatshirt fabric made from a cotton blend with a zip down the front that continues down one leg and ribbing around the neckline, cuffs and hems. The zip has a chin guard. Soft brushed inside. The cotton content of all-in-one suit is organic.
Leggings in soft, supple leather with a thin cotton lining. High waist with concealed elastication, a zip at one side and legs with decorative seams and raw-edge hems.
Shirt in an airy cotton weave with a collar and buttons down the front. Chest pocket, buttoned cuffs and a rounded hem. Longer at the back.
T-shirt in printed cotton with a wider neckline. Slightly longer at the back.

Shirt in an airy cotton weave with a turn-down collar, open chest pocket and yoke at the back. Long sleeves with a tab and button and adjustable buttoning at the cuffs, and a rounded hem. Regular Fit – a classic fit with good room for movement and a gently tapered waist to create a comfortable, tailored silhouette.
Joggers in soft sweatshirt fabric with an elasticated drawstring waist, side pockets and ribbed hems. Soft brushed inside.
Satin nightslip with narrow shoulder straps that cross at the back and a V-neck with a wide lace trim.
T-shirt in soft, organic cotton jersey with a narrow trim around the neckline. Slightly longer and rounded at the back.
T-shirt in soft, patterned cotton jersey.
5-pocket jeans in washed, stretch denim with a regular waist, zip fly and button, and skinny legs.

Tailored trousers in woven fabric with a key chain. High waist with pleats at the front and covered elastication at the back, zip fly with a button, side pockets, a fake back pocket and wide, gently flared legs.
Derby shoes in shiny imitation leather with a text print, lacing at the top and gently rounded toes. Canvas linings and insoles and rubber soles. Heel approx. 3.5 cm.
Shorts in soft cotton jersey with an elasticated, drawstring waist.
5-pocket jeans in washed, superstretch denim with a regular waist, zip fly and button, and skinny legs.
Long-sleeved top in soft jersey.
Short-sleeved lace top with an opening at the back and button at the back of the neck. Raw scalloped edges at the cuffs and hem.
Cold shoulder top in soft viscose jersey with raw edges at the top, narrow shoulder straps, short sleeves and gently rounded hem. Longer at the back.

Biker jacket in slightly stretchy twill made from a cotton blend. Notch lapels with a decorative metal button, a diagonal zip down the front, zipped front pockets and a decorative tab and metal press-stud at the sides. Lined.
Shoulder bag in grained imitation leather. One zipped inner compartment and a zip and detachable, adjustable shoulder strap at the top. Lined. Size 4.5x14x22.5 cm.
Knee-length coat in soft felted fabric with notch lapels, concealed press-studs down the front, pockets in the side seams and a straight-cut hem. Lined.
Jeans in washed, stretch denim with a high waist, zip fly and button, back pockets and slim legs reversible sequin side stripes.
Leggings in soft, printed cotton jersey with an elasticated waist.
Round-necked T-shirt in cotton jersey with a decorative seam at the top.
Pyjamas in soft jersey. Wide, short-sleeved top with a print motif on the front. Short shorts with an elasticated drawstring waist.
5-pocket, knee-length denim skirt with a raw-edge hem.
Long mesh skirt with embroidery, wide elastication at the waist and a concealed zip in one side. Jersey underskirt.
Jumper in a textured cotton knit containing some wool with ribbing around the neckline, cuffs and hem.
Fitted jersey top with narrow shoulder straps.
Jumper in a soft rib knit with long sleeves.
Top in soft cotton jersey with a slightly wider neckline, long sleeves and a rounded hem.
Jacket in supersoft pile. Hood with appliqués, a zip down the front with a chin guard, and kangaroo pockets. Unlined.
Fully lined bikini. Flounced top with narrow shoulder straps with a small metal decoration attached to one strap. Matching bottoms.
Top in a soft, gently draping silk and cotton blend with gently dropped shoulders and long sleeves. Ribbing around the neckline, cuffs and hem.
Trainers in scuba fabric and mesh with a rubber section that extends across the foot with lacing and around the back of the heel. Mesh linings and insoles and rubber soles.
Slides with crossover straps in imitation leather at the front, moulded imitation suede insoles and fluted ethylene-vinyl acetate (EVA) soles.

Trousers in woven fabric with an adjustable, elasticated waist, zip fly and button, side pockets and pockets with a button at the back. Adjustable elastic braces with imitation leather details that can be unbuttoned and removed.
Slim-fit trousers in soft, superstretch twill for maximum mobility. Adjustable elasticated waist (in sizes 8-12Y), a zip fly and button, fake front pockets, real back pockets and straight hems.
Cropped top in soft cotton jersey with concealed elastication at the front of the top.
Leggings with wide elastication at the waist.
A-line dress in soft, jacquard-knit jersey made from a cotton blend with long sleeves, fake welt front pockets, a ribbed neckline, and press-studs on one shoulder.
T-shirt in printed cotton jersey.

Cropped, boxy top in lightweight sweatshirt fabric made from a cotton blend with a V-neck, low dropped shoulder seams and long, wide sleeves. Ribbing around the neckline, cuffs and hem. The polyester content of the top is recycled.
Short, straight dress in a printed viscose crêpe weave with a round neck, opening with a button at the back of the neck and short sleeves.
Vest top in cotton jersey with a print motif and deep armholes with raw edges.
Hammered metal hair clips. Length 6.5 cm.
Short, off-the-shoulder flounced dress woven in a textured Tencel™ lyocell blend with narrow adjustable shoulder straps and short sleeves with elastication at the top. Lined.
Fitted off-the-shoulder top in soft jersey with a lace-trimmed V-neck and long sleeves.
Tailored trousers in a sturdy textured weave with a zip fly and concealed hook-and-eye fastener. Side pockets, fake back pockets and straight-cut legs that taper to the hem with creases.
Double-layered hat in a soft, fine knit containing glittery threads with a reversible sequin motif on the front (sizes 1½-4Y with normal sequins).
Short-sleeved top in soft cotton jersey with a frill at the top that continues over the shoulders.
Shirt in imitation leather with a collar, concealed press-studs down the front, and slits in the sides. Long sleeves and cuffs with a concealed press-stud. Brushed inside.

Non-wired bra in an airy silk blend with lace sections. Lined cups that give the bust a natural shape and provide light support, adjustable spaghetti shoulder straps, an elasticated hem and a narrow hook-and-eye fastening at the back.
Fully lined bikini bottoms with a low waist and lace-trimmed flounce at the top.
